{"tid":1011854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一家外出拜年　電線短路焚宅","createTime":"2019-02-07T06:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T07:35:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e59698dc2c9857d52f56426762ad08397f7792c8","tid":1011854,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190207/20607790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190207%2F20607790&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=d02e4d20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190207%2F20607790&h=a6e3873f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190207/20607790</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年02月07日 <br />\n<br />\n一家外出拜年　電線短路焚宅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190207/large/07la6p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190207%2Flarge%2F07la6p04.jpg&h=b7d68f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消防員接報到場，升起雲梯向起火單位射水灌救。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日年初二，秀茂坪曉麗苑一單位一家四口外出拜年，屋內一房間疑因電掣電線短路引起火警，消防員到場破門射水灌救，十多分鐘後將火救熄，但起火房間已遭嚴重焚毀。火警中無人受傷，約半百住客自行疏散至地面暫避。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n50住客疏散<br />\n<br />\n現場為曉麗苑曉安閣7樓一單位，住有一家四口，據鄰居稱，出事單位一家人昨早上出門，相信是往親友家拜年。至下午3時25分，該單位閉門失火，有濃煙冒出窗外，途人及鄰居發現紛紛報警。消防員接報到場，升起一條雲梯向起火單位射水灌救，一隊煙帽隊員則破門入內救火及查看是否有人被困屋內，火勢於十多分鐘後被救熄，其中一間細房遭嚴重焚毀，一部冷氣機被燒爛，單位外牆被熏黑。其間，約50名大廈住客自行疏散落地面暫避。<br />\n<br />\n火警中無人受傷，消防員進入起火單位調查後，懷疑是細房一個電掣的電線短路，火花燃着旁邊雜物引起火警，因當時屋內無人，直至濃煙湧出屋外始被街外人發現。火警並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n■記者溫瑞麟  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n凌志撞壆起火　兩人及時脫困<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n市民擅放煙花　危及馬鐵安全"},{"pid":"d7067942abea64b235f5a977b5a5774e627de330","tid":1011854,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"富貴榮華"},{"pid":"a651e5eb3c00f73011871d678ae4855984ded33a","tid":1011854,"uid":59536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:21:02.000Z","msg":"豬籠入水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653fb768d73369afa7278cfc8728acaceca4258b","tid":1011854,"uid":181697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"花開富貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n消防真係忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83f98e8bbc15d4b1e3d9b0359f95751913c6201","tid":1011854,"uid":210265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"我住隔離座d煙都入哂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472d380e2056919e05ab380252df860782f3bc2e","tid":1011854,"uid":6104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"在<br />\n、他：他"},{"pid":"f8744e813c004431ce3c33415732c6031c912ed3","tid":1011854,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d83f98e8bbc15d4b1e3d9b0359f95751913c6201","tid":1011854,"uid":210265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"我住隔離座d煙都入哂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276da04b155e63e89b74ac7949b4850843fe8956","tid":1011854,"uid":185651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8f8584d8540b4b64d2e1ad29e65457b22a2628","tid":1011854,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d83f98e8bbc15d4b1e3d9b0359f95751913c6201","tid":1011854,"uid":210265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T06:53:02.000Z","msg":"我住隔離座d煙都入哂嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces